# Component and Page Entry Files

When adding or refactoring components/pages, ensure the folder name matches the component/page name and the entry file is `index.tsx`.

Inside `src/pages`, omit the `Page` suffix from folder names and component names (the route implies it).

```typescript
// Example structure:
// DetailCard/
//   index.tsx
//   styles.ts
//
// Pages:
// src/pages/Dashboard/
//   index.tsx (const Dashboard)
//   DashboardCards/index.tsx
```
